\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4.8}{\ignorespaces Pipeline execution model. Each localisation request is dispatched as a sequence of \texttt  {AsyncCommand} objects to an asynchronous task queue, which executes them in a dedicated worker thread pool. GPU-resident stages (FoundationStereo inference and 3DGS rendering) are protected by a semaphore concurrency guard. Incoming requests are queued independently, ensuring each observation is processed in full.}}{80}{}\protected@file@percent }
